author: rwhitcomb
msg: PIVOT-933: Allow a tree view branch listener to veto a branch expand or collapse
or defer until later, similarly to Rollup expansion changes or Accordion selection
changes.  Two new methods are added to TreeViewBranchListener to accommodate this:
processing in TreeView.setExpanded and in the existing skin: TerraTreeViewSkin.
Add the new methods to TreeViewBranchListener.Adapter with appropriate default
Verified correct operation in a test application, and verified the Javadoc.
